25/08/2003
SHANGHAI, China -- Visiting Shanghai on Saturday (23 August), Romanian President Ion Iliescu said Romanian companies could provide construction services for the 2008 Summer Olympics in Beijing.
He also reiterated calls for Chinese companies to invest in Romania, saying this would facilitate entry into the European market.
Iliescu is making an extended official visit to China.
(ACT Media, Rompres - 25/08/03)
